  "time_ut": 1661144659,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d89\u0da7\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The goals that the President took over the country are being fulfilled",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Deputy Leader and President's Senior Advisor Mr. Ruwan Wijayawardena said that the goals that President Ranil Wickramasinghe took over the country are being fulfilled little by little today.",
        "Saying that the president took over the country to build the economy, Mr. Wijayawardena said that today the old fuel queues and gas queues are gone and the country is undergoing normalization.",
        "Mr. Ruwan Wijayawardena said that former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa requested many party leaders to take over the country and solve the economic crisis, but none of them responded, so the current President Ranil Wickramasinghe took over the country.",
        "Mr. Vijayawardena also mentioned that Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe has arranged to provide fertilizers for the farmers in discussion with India.",
        "Mr. Ruwan Vijayawardena said this while addressing the Anuradhapura District Development Council."
      ],
